{"tid":636324,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"不滿駐華使館道路控制權受限　英國拒華使館進駐新址","createTime":"2018-04-20T17:45:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-22T07:21:59.000Z","uid":5195,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"d7ccf424d27a9a980d3b9114d42f3e9320208e9b","tid":636324,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T17:45:21.000Z","msg":"英國傳媒周四（19日）報道引述消息人士指，英國決定拒絕向中國提供全新的駐倫敦大使館選址。報道又指，除非中國願意放棄對英國駐北京大使館附近的控制權，否則相關官員不會讓中國大使館，移至位於倫敦塔附近的舊皇家鑄幣廠。<br />\n<br />\n報道引述消息指，迄今為止，中方一直拒絕放棄對英國駐北京大使館附近道路的控制權，此舉已觸怒英國外交部。據悉中國計劃將其大使館從倫敦市中心馬里波恩（Marylebone），搬到約60萬平方英尺的舊皇家鑄幣廠。"},{"pid":"a2c7cd3c9ee46e8c643287503c1b372fd2627f4f","tid":636324,"uid":141151,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T17:54:19.000Z","msg":"中国又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16630f5926c70f76e5f56e2d582fa6d115679516","tid":636324,"uid":40628,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T17:56:51.000Z","msg":"藍絲繼續認做中國人啦，威震全球 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"539e57b94d53b342c919d430a11107012a592666","tid":636324,"uid":134323,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T17:57:32.000Z","msg":"驅逐使館管 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0428962a82817bde71e47b00871d30fbb033e2a4","tid":636324,"uid":91721,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T18:03:55.000Z","msg":"駛中國嘅第一巨艦去台海再噴黑煙，仲唔嚇到班淨係識飲茶嘅英國佬賴屎?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e5d0c8242cc96453c8005d56c582f490c9c8b39","tid":636324,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T02:04:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e40c50d56817f34051ebeb03f4b7aa119a519583","tid":636324,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T06:23:22.000Z","msg":"你做初一"},{"pid":"d1d77a